import React from "react"
import ReactDOM from "react-dom"
import { BrowserRouter } from "react-router-dom"
import "./index.css"
import App from "./App"
import ProductsProvider from "./context/products-context"

ReactDOM.render(
	<ProductsProvider>
		<BrowserRouter>
			<App />
		</BrowserRouter>
	</ProductsProvider>,

	document.getElementById("root")
)
